values: Yeah, I love Thanksgiving but am very glad it is done and over with! I had it at my house for the first time ever and it was very stressful. And then not only did i have to deal with it thursday but we had another one at our house saturday (yesterday) with my husbands family who couldn't make it. Talk about being good on eating turkey for a while. Now i get to do it all over again Christmas boy oh boy. It took me forever to clean! My husband can do it all Christmas. Not really i can't do that to him, I'll help! Something that really bugged me though is the fact that every year my family has it at one of their houses i am always there early to help and i always stay and help clean. The only person that showed up to help was my mom. And no one helped clean. It kinda pissed me off because i cooked all day and went out of my way to make things nice for everyone and no one could even help me clean. So when they have the holidays at their houses in the future i am going to show them the same courtesy of not helping them clean. I will just say thank you and leave like they did me! I usually can't wait for christmas to come and fear for it to be over because i love it so much, but this year i can wait for it to come and fear for it not to be over fast enough. I know i sound like a humbug, but really i am not. My little girl makes me so happy that seeing her happy makes me have a better feeling towards everything! It just sucks that i am not looking forward to christmas just for the fact that no one will even help me clean! I'll live though! I just feel like half of my life is spent on cleaning anyways that it sux ass to add to it! Oh well. My husband tries to help but he is a procrastinator and wants to do it tomorrow and then sit around before getting to it that i already have everything done before he gets around to helping which is probably done on purpose, but oh well i love him still. But i am done with bitching and feel better now that i got this out now i can have a better attitude toward christmas and just go with the flow. Christmas i'll just ask if since i always help them if they can help me! Well peace and joy for the holidays everyone!

I got the new evanessance cd today, and it rocks!!! I love evanessance. Nickelbacks new cd rocks too, along with my chemical romance, it also rocks. I highly recommend buying all three of those cds. And if you don't like them then you are just weird. I love listening to music it helps me with many things. For example, when i need to clean if i pop in some music it help to motivate me, and when i am driving in a car it helps calm me. It's weird how one thing can help me in different ways! Music is bad ass and the people who do it i give mad kuddos to! I wish i could be that talented. I have always wanted to learn to play guitar. All of them acoustic, eletric, bass....
I want to many things out of life. I have a problem but i deal with it. I just want to do so many things and one life time is not long enough to do them. Well actually it probably is, but i also other problems called motivation and laziness. They don't mix well with all i am trying to do. I just can't help it. Its hard enough for me to find the energy to clean, do laundry, play with my kid, and take car of my family! I think it is a health problem, i really do because i have tried energy boosters and everything to try to help and nothing works. I should probably ask a professional. It might also be my diet, but i have a pretty well balanced diet, so i really don't know, but wish i would get it figured out! It's weird cuz when i was a teenager i couldn't sit down, and now it's different the sad part is i am not much older than a teenager, and i know having a kid takes alot out of you, but come on i had her 3 years ago. My body definately has healed from my baby girl. May it's mental, maybe i need to be more motivated mentally, but i don't think so because i really do feel it in my body, my body always feels tired. and actually what sucks is my mind seems like it's never tired. It like the energizer bunny (you know the rest)! But i will be laying in bed usually for a long time, my kid and husband and alot of people i know can just fall right to sleep. I just lay there for hours thinking about shit and it's not shit i am stressing about either. It's just weird out of the blue shit (which is another topic some other time)! But it's just craziness. But enough of this. Later.

Okay so i have been sick for like 2 weeks now, and instead of getting better i am getting worse. I am in the middle of moving, well we are almost done, tomorrow is the last day we will have to move anything, then i can finish unpacking and it will be all peachy. It just sucks that i am sick during all of it and i am probably getting worse because i am not resting properly. But it sucks and i would rather be sick any other time except for now. It makes moving that much harder but atleast it will be over soon and i will probably feel better once we are done moving and i can rest. I really don't want to be at work, i am going to try to get off early. We'll see dave (my co-worker) might not let me but maybe? He sometimes suprises me and shows me the "big heart" everyone tells me he has. But i am going to go sorry to bitch to everyone but it helps me!!!

Okay so to me huge fancy expensive weddings are pointless. Yes getting married is a big deal but you should not have to make your parents or you go broke over it. I am happily married and didn't have a huge expensive wedding, which i am very grateful over because well with the money spent on a wedding you could buy a brand new car. I don't know about you but i would rather invest my money into something that will last longer than a day. Weddings are nice but keep them less expensive people cuz no matter what they all mean the same thing! If your going to spend alot of money on your wedding, spend it on the honey moon!!! hell yeah!!!

Okay, so i am new to this, my friend amanda told me it was nice so i am trying it out. My life has been kinda stressful lately and i think this will help me to get my stress out so i am not taking it out at home. But not now, this entry is just to say hi and will write later. bye.
